---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" size="2.5rem" rainbow />
		<h2 set:html={"Rust&nbsp;&amp;<br>WebAssembly"} />
		<p>Author of the MoonZoon web framework and Boon â€” a programming language with a Rust runtime and hardware synthesis.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="pencil-line" size="2.5rem" rainbow />
		<h2 set:html={"Product&nbsp;&amp;<br>UX&nbsp;Design"} />
		<p>Design of business software and developer tools, including the NovyWave waveform visualizer.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="rocket-launch" size="2.5rem" rainbow />
		<h2 set:html={"Developer<br>Experience"} />
		<p>Examples, playgrounds, and clear APIs that make software easy to adopt.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
		max-width: 24rem;
		margin-inline: auto;
	}

	.skills > div {
		text-align: center;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 0.75rem;
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 2rem;
			max-width: none;
		}

		.skills > div {
			text-align: left;
			align-items: flex-start;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}

	@media (min-width: 70em) {
		.box {
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			gap: 5rem;
		}
	}
</style>
